<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
    <title>
        <%= brand %> — Ethical Cybersecurity Training
    </title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #0b0f14;
            --card: #0f1420;
            --muted: #93a0b4;
            --text: #e9eef7;
            --primary: #7c3aed;
            --accent: #22d3ee;
            --outline: #1e2635;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box
        }

        html,
        body {
            height: 100%
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, Segoe UI, Inter, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial;
            color: var(--text);
            background:
                radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 75% -10%, rgba(34, 211, 238, .15), transparent 60%),
                radial-gradient(900px 500px at 10% 110%, rgba(124, 58, 237, .18), transparent 60%),
                var(--bg);
        }

        /* navbar */
        .nav {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 10;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 16px 22px;
            background: rgba(11, 15, 20, .6);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--outline);
        }

        .brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: .3px
        }

        .badge {
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: conic-gradient(from 210deg, var(--accent), var(--primary));
            box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(124, 58, 237, .35), inset 0 0 14px rgba(34, 211, 238, .25);
        }

        .login {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text);
            font-weight: 600;
            border: 1px solid var(--outline);
            padding: 8px 14px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: .18s ease;
        }

        .login:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(34, 211, 238, .12);
        }

        /* hero */
        .wrap {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 42px 20px 72px;
        }

        .card {
            margin-top: 28px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, .02), rgba(255, 255, 255, .0));
            border: 1px solid var(--outline);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 28px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, .35);
        }

        .title {
            font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 56px);
            line-height: 1.06;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: .2px;
        }

        .gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--primary));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(124, 58, 237, .25);
        }

        .subtitle {
            margin-top: 14px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: clamp(14px, 2.2vw, 18px);
            max-width: 60ch;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 16px;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            margin-top: 26px;
        }

        .pill {
            background: var(--card);
            border: 1px solid var(--outline);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 16px;
        }

        .pill h3 {
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
            font-size: 18px
        }

        .pill p {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 14px
        }

        .footnote {
            margin-top: 22px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 12px
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="nav">
        <div class="brand"><span class="badge"></span>
            <%= brand %>
        </div>
        <a class="login" href="/login">Login</a>
    </nav>

    <main class="wrap">
        <section class="card">
            <h1 class="title">
                From <span class="gradient">rookie</span> to <span class="gradient">ethical red-teamer</span>.
            </h1>
            <p class="subtitle">
                Hands-on training in reconnaissance, web exploitation, privilege escalation, and responsible disclosure.
                Learn the offensive mindset—applied ethically—to help secure real systems.
            </p>

            <div class="grid">
                <div class="pill">
                    <h3>Foundations</h3>
                    <p>Linux, networking, threat models, and lab setup you’ll actually use.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="pill">
                    <h3>Web & API</h3>
                    <p>SSTI, auth flaws, SQLi, SSRF, file-upload risks, and modern defenses.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="pill">
                    <h3>Privilege Escalation</h3>
                    <p>Windows & Linux privesc, misconfig chains, and credential hygiene.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="pill">
                    <h3>Ops & Reporting</h3>
                    <p>Scoping, notes, reproducible PoCs, and professional remediation advice.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="footnote">
                Training is for lawful, ethical security testing only. Always get written authorization.
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>

</html>